snippet: Colorado's Civil Rights Commission on Friday ordered a baker to make wedding cakes for same-sex couples, finding his religious objections to the practice did not trump the state's anti-discrimination statutes....

headline.print_headline: Panel: Baker Must Make Cakes for Gay Weddings
headline.main: Panel: Baker Must Make Cakes for Gay Weddings

lead_paragraph: Colorado's Civil Rights Commission on Friday ordered a baker to make wedding cakes for same-sex couples, finding his religious objections to the practice did not trump the state's anti-discrimination statutes.
